  <tbody>
    <tr style="background:#f0fdf4;"><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; width:45%;">可以便宜一点吗？</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Can you make it cheaper?</td></tr>
    <tr><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">最低多少？</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">What's your lowest price?</td></tr>
    <tr style="background:#f0fdf4;"><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">买多一点可以打折吗？</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Discount for buying more?</td></tr>
    <tr><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">那边更便宜。</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">It's cheaper over there.</td></tr>
    <tr style="background:#f0fdf4;"><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">朋友价吧！</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Give me the friend price!</td></tr>
    <tr><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">老板，算便宜一点嘛。</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Boss, give me a better deal.</td></tr>
