<p><strong>Online shopping vocabulary:</strong> E-commerce is massive in Chinese-speaking markets, and knowing the key terms helps whether you are browsing from abroad or shopping locally. The biggest platforms are <strong>淘宝</strong> (Táobǎo), <strong>京东</strong> (Jīngdōng / JD.com), and <strong>拼多多</strong> (Pīnduōduō) in mainland China, and <strong>虾皮</strong> (Xiāpí / Shopee) in Taiwan. Here are the essential online shopping terms:</p>

